ai.chat.intro: Hello! Welcome to the OpenWES Q&A assistant. I am an AI assistant designed to answer your questions about the Open Warehouse Execution System.
ai.chat.topics: Explain features and settings in OpenWES
Guide you on optimizing warehouse processes and efficiency
Provide troubleshooting advice and technical support
Share best practices and industry trends
Answer specific questions about inventory management and order processing
ai.chat.quickStartContent: Simply type your question or choose a topic, and I will provide detailed information and solutions immediately. Whether you're facing technical challenges or looking to improve operational efficiency, I'm here to assist you.
ai.chat.enhanceContent: With me, you can get instant help and support, ensuring smooth warehouse operations. Let's work together to improve your warehouse management experience!
ai.chat.closing: How can I assist you today? Or would you like to learn about specific aspects first?
